<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.7">
<l>paṭaittiṭ ṭativvai yamuyya muṉanāḷ paṇintēt tavallār tuyarā yavellām</l>
<l>tuṭaittiṭ ṭavarait taṉakkāk kaveṉṉat teḷiyā varakkar tiṟalpō yaviya</l>
<l>miṭaittiṭ ṭeḻunta kuraṅkaip paṭaiyā vilaṅkal pukappāyc civimma kaṭalai</l>
<l>yaṭaittiṭ ṭavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇ ṇeyuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having created this earth long ago to save it, utterly wiping out</l>
<l rend="indent">all that becomes a sorrow of those able to bow and praise [him],</l>
<l>Since he thought to make them his own, the one who blocked up the sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">so the power of the ignorant demons was extinguished, vanishing,</l>
<l>By means of a legion of monkeys who appeared being pressed [in a crowd]</l>
<l rend="indent">dropping hills into [the sea] so it was full,</l>
<l>See, he is the one who was bound, having eaten the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">churned by the herder women today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
